title: S- no mastery 6 token
body: I just played diana, got S- but didn't get my mastery 6 token, yes she is mastery 5 yes i have already got a mastery 6 token. it was in the new gamemode, but if its calculating mastery score, why didn't it give me my token

replies.body: Featured gamemodes do not provide mastery tokens, only normal/ranked games on summoners rift do.
